name: The Mermaid's Guise
description:
#4 | Ahmad Abi M Sidik | Nov 2021

In fairy tales, we are always told that mermaids are beautiful and kind creatures. But in this picture, you will know that the beautiful mermaid is just a Fishbone Demon (Siluman Tulang Ikan). The electric eel can see the decay that the mermaid hides.
